    <p>NEW YORK • The Char­lotte Hor­nets said on Sun­day they have ac­quired for­ward Gor­don Hay­ward in a sign-and-trade deal from the Bos­ton Celtics.</p>
    <p>The Na­tional Bas­ket­ball As­so­ci­a­tion team, who are owned by Michael Jor­dan, will re­ceive a 2023 and 2024 se­cond-round draft pick in re­turn for a pro­tected 2022 se­cond-round draft pick.</p>


